"title": "5780: advisers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5780: advisers",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Those who give advice and counsel. Human advice is desirable, but not always reliable. Only God's counsel is wholly dependable.</p>\n<h2>Human advisers</h2>\n<h3>It is wise to consult advisers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:22\">PRO 15:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:15\">PRO 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:10\">PRO 13:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:12\">PRO 15:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:20\">PRO 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:18\">PRO 20:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:6\">PRO 24:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:13\">ECC 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>It is folly to reject wise advisers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:14\">PRO 11:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:8\">1KI 12:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:8\">2CH 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:13-1Kgs12:15\">1KI 12:13–12:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:13-2Chr10:15\">2CH 10:13–10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:25-Prov1:26\">PRO 1:25–1:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:30-Prov1:31\">PRO 1:30–1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:18\">JER 18:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:11\">ACT 27:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:21\">ACT 27:21</a></p>\n<h3>Unwise advisers are dangerous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1\">PSA 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:16\">JOB 21:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:7\">JOB 42:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:5\">PRO 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:11\">ISA 19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:2-Ezek11:4\">EZK 11:2–11:4</a></p>\n<h3>Advisers who trust in false gods must be rejected</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:19-Isa8:20\">ISA 8:19–8:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:15-2Chr25:16\">2CH 25:15–25:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:3\">ISA 19:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:13-Isa47:15\">ISA 47:13–47:15</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of wise advisers</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:17-Exod18:24\">EXO 18:17–18:24</a> <em>Jethro</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:23\">DAN 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:48\">DAN 2:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:18\">DAN 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:27\">DAN 4:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:11-Dan5:12\">DAN 5:11–5:12</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:38-Acts5:39\">ACT 5:38–5:39</a> <em>Gamaliel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:10-2Cor8:12\">2CO 8:10–8:12</a> <em>Paul</em></p>\n<h2>Examples of bad advisers</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:16\">NUM 31:16</a> <em>Balaam</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:31\">2SA 15:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:1\">2SA 17:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:7\">2SA 17:7</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:28-1Kgs12:30\">1KI 12:28–12:30</a> <em>Jeroboam</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:11\">ISA 19:11</a> <em>Egyptian advisers</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:49-John11:53\">JHN 11:49–11:53</a> <em>Caiaphas</em></p>\n<h2>Examples of official advisers</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:26\">GEN 26:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:12\">2SA 15:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:23\">2SA 16:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:5\">1KI 4:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:32-1Chr27:33\">1CH 27:32–27:33</a></p>\n<h2>God as adviser</h2>\n<h3>God is an adviser</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:7\">PSA 16:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:5\">1KI 22:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:4\">2CH 18:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:8\">PSA 32:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:24\">PSA 73:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:18\">REV 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>The promised Messiah is an adviser</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6\">ISA 9:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit is an adviser</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16\">JHN 14:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a> <em>The Holy Spirit's counsel defends believers from every accusation and provides all necessary teaching and guidance.</em></p>",
